pnap:index/ipBlock:IpBlock.description:
Provides a phoenixNAP IP Block resource. This can be used to create, modify and delete IP Blocks.



{{% examples %}}
## Example Usage
{{% example %}}

Create an IP Block 

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as pnap from "@pulumi/pnap";

// Create an IP Block
const ip_block_1 = new pnap.IpBlock("ip-block-1", {
    cidrBlockSize: "/28",
    description: "IP Block #1 used for publicly accessing server #1.",
    location: "PHX",
    tags: [
        {
            tagAssignment: {
                name: "tag-1",
                value: "PROD",
            },
        },
        {
            tagAssignment: {
                name: "tag-2",
            },
        },
    ],
});
```
